From 9408805c27c86f48f35dd9bc30a54d957d264a01 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tavidee Hoskins <246332205+tavideehoskins@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Wed, 3 Jun 2026 10:29:23 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Add rec UI redesign prototype (/rec-demo + standalone build)

Clickable prototype of the proposed 3-level recommendation output
(School card -> Programs + school sections -> per-program accordion),
using hardcoded SLU BSN exemplar-v7 data. No Notion calls, no live
routes changed.

- components/rec_demo: core (page + hierarchy), charts (Recharts:
  salary-vs-CoL bars + financial-aid waterfall), data (hardcoded
  exemplar), interface, standalone entry
- router: add unauthenticated /rec-demo route
- shadow-cljs.edn: SPA push-state fallback for dev-http; :rec-demo
  standalone build target for static hosting
- rec-demo-site/index.html: host template for the static demo

Live demo: https://tavideehoskins.github.io/bryc-rec-demo/

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
